| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4706 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3e4b38aa-61c7-5b0c-bfd1-aa9118b4c4dc"
